{
  "stem": "13469.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We'd never seen anything like a trolley bus, before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But they run very near to us in Willesden kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You'll remember those.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And with Ruti, we used to play in the streets kind of thing, pretending to be trolley buses, with bits of cardboard in front of us and destinations-- [LAUGHS] boards on it, and those sort of things.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we had a good time in England.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But, of course, we didn't have our father with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We went to various friends and relatives of Uncle Rudi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there, Ruti had the-- another hole in his head.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was always pushing him, and shoving him around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he always had some bandages around his head kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The, the first time was in the back garden in Berlin, when I pushed him out of our sandpit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he had a big hole in his head.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the second time was in Ostend when we're trying to catch the boat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I pulled him along a bit too fast, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he fell over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he had another hole in his head.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then, in London, we were at some friends of Rudi and Lotte's who had a swimming pool in the background.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I pushed him into the swimming pool.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he had another hole in his head.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he was-- we always have pictures of him with a big bandage around his head.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I think now I was a bit hard on him, I suppose, in those days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But everything was all right there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "The, the really major event that happened to us in London was that my sister, Eve, was born.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "On the 23rd of June, 1936, she was born.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And she was christened-- or she was named Rachel Eve Dorothy Oppenheimer.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
